<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Mainz</head><p>Der Rat bittet um Auskunft über die Meinung der Kurfürsten nach dem Tod des Markgrafen Jobst von Mähren.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_227" id="113r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_227_r1l6">Meintʒe / </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_227_r1l7"><expan>Lıeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>fr<ex>ewnde</ex></expan> / von der lewffe <expan>vveg<ex>en</ex></expan> / die <expan>ÿetʒund<ex>en</ex></expan> in dem Reiche ſind / </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_227_r1l8">vnd <expan>beſund<ex>er</ex></expan> als nuͦ <expan>vveilund<ex>en</ex></expan> / <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> hochgeborn fürſt vnd <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> / Margraf </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_227_r1l9">Joſt / von <expan>Meͣrh<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ſeliger gedechtnüſſe / <expan>abgang<ex>en</ex></expan> iſt / den etliche <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>e</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_227_r1l10"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> die kürfürſten/ gewelet <expan>het<ex>en</ex></expan> / <expan>Roga<ex>mus</ex></expan> / Ob Jr iht vveſt / <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> fürbaʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_227_r1l11">erfüret / vvie ſich <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> / die kürfürſten / <expan>darvnt<ex>er</ex></expan> cʒu halten mainten / </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_227_r1l12">daʒ Jr vns das / vnd vvas Jr auch ſuſt / treͣfflichs <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>ſöliche<ex>n</ex></expan> lewffen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_227_r1l13">weſt / <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> erfüret / <expan>ÿetʒund<ex>en</ex></expan> beÿ <expan>diſ<ex>em</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> boten / <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>nach</expan> beÿ <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> ſelbs </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_227_r1l14">boten / alſvil dann <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>vveiſh<ex>eit</ex></expan> davon <expan>fügliche<ex>n</ex></expan> ſeÿ cʒu <expan>ſchreibe<ex>n</ex></expan> / <expan>wiſʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_227_r1l15">laſʒen / vnd <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchreıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wöllet / Als etc vnd das in <expan>ſoliche<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd andern </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_227_r1l16">ſachen etc <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>Sup<ex>ra</ex></expan> $ </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_227" id="113r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Meincze </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, von der lewffe
                            <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, die <expan>yeczund<ex>en</ex></expan> in
                        dem reiche sind und <expan>besund<ex>er</ex></expan>, als nuͦ
                                <expan>weilund<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> hochgeborn fürst und
                            <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> margraf Jost von
                            <expan>Meͣrh<ex>er</ex>n</expan> seliger gedechtnüsse
                                <expan>abgang<ex>en</ex></expan> ist, den etliche
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>e</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> die kürfürsten gewelet
                            <expan>het<ex>en</ex></expan>. <expan>Roga<ex>mus</ex></expan>, ob ir
                        iht west <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> fürbaz erfüret, wie sich
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> die kürfürsten
                            <expan>darunt<ex>er</ex></expan> czu halten mainten, daz ir uns das und,
                        was ir auch sust treͣfflichs <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>söliche<ex>n</ex></expan> lewffen west <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        erfüret, <expan>yeczund<ex>en</ex></expan> bey <expan>dis<ex>em</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan> boten <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>nach</expan> bey <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> selbs boten,
                        alsvil dann <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>weish<ex>eit</ex></expan> davon <expan>fügliche<ex>n</ex></expan> sey
                        czu <expan>schreibe<ex>n</ex></expan>, <expan>wisze<ex>n</ex></expan> laszen
                        und <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schreib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wöllet. Als etc. Und das
                        in <expan>soliche<ex>n</ex></expan> und andern sachen etc.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>sup<ex>ra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
